Interface Callable <p>实现Callable接口，封装成FutureTask对象</p> <p>将FutureTask对象给Thread对象</p> <pre><code>FutureTask&lt;String&gt; futureTask = new FutureTask&lt;&gt;(new CallableDemo());

Thread td = new Thread(futureTask);

td.start();

try {
    System.out.println(futureTask.get());
} catch (InterruptedException | ExecutionException e) {
    throw new RuntimeException(e);
}
</code></pre>  <p>Annotation</p> <p><code>Thread.sleep(int mils)</code>线程休眠，毫秒</p> <p><code>Thread.this.join()</code>让线程插队，在当前线程中强制让别的线程执行完毕</p>

同步代码块 <pre><code>synchronized(this) {
    //some code here
}
</code></pre> <p>同步代码块实例方法尽量使用<code>this</code>做锁，静态方法使用<code>ClassName.class</code>做锁</p>

同步方法 用<code>synchronized</code>来给方法加锁 <pre><code>public synchronized void funcName() {
    //function code here
}
</code></pre> <p>同步方法默认实例方法用<code>this</code>做锁，静态方法用<code>ClassName.class</code>做锁</p>

Lock锁 <pre><code>    private final Lock lock = new ReentrantLock();

    public void doSomeThing() {
        //some code
        try {
            lock.lock();
            //some code
        } finally {
            lock.unlock();
        }
    }
</code></pre>

